ema]] (65), Ugandan afro-pop singer and guitarist ** [[Vinnie Paul]] (54), American metal drummer ([[Pantera]], [[Damageplan]], [[Hellyeah]]) * '''24''' – George Cameron (70), American baroque pop drummer ([[The Left Banke]]) * '''26''' ** [[Fedor Frešo]] (71), Slovak rock bassist ([[The Soulmen]], [[Prúdy]]) ** [[Ed Simons (conductor)|Ed Simons]] (101), American classical music conductor * '''27''' – [[Steve Soto]] (54), American punk rock bassist ([[Adolescents (band)|Adolescents]], [[Agent Orange (band)|Agent Orange]], [[Manic Hispanic]]) * '''29''' – Eugene Pitt (80), American doo wop singer ([[The Jive Five]]) * '''30''' – Dean Webb (81), American bluegrass mandolinist ([[The Dillards]])
